<subSubSection id="EBF5653D9E48FF80FFC97536FDCA1237" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="A35036B69E48FF80FFC97536FE101554" blockId="76.[93,620,213,1147]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">
COMMENTS: Brehm, in the original description, noted that his son had shot a male and two females on the 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FE387573FD9D1733" box="[395,619,360,382]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1847-12-28">28 December 1847</date>
and that he had obtained a first-year male on 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FFEE75B9FEC417F5" box="[93,306,419,441]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1848-02-12">12 February 1848</date>
that had been shot a few days before. 
<bibRefCitation id="C77E4B479E48FF80FF4375DBFE49179A" author="Hartert, E." box="[240,447,449,471]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" pagination="4 - 63" refId="ref118974" refString="Hartert, E. 1918. Types of birds in the Tring Museum. A. Types in the Brehm Collection. Novitates Zoologicae 25: 4 - 63." type="journal article" year="1918">Hartert (1918: 11)</bibRefCitation>
listed the male collected on 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FF4375C4FE3117BE" box="[240,455,478,500]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1847-12-27">27 December 1847</date>
as the type of 
<taxonomicName id="64EF4D359E48FF80FFEE75E6FF69145C" authorityName="C. L. Brehm" authorityYear="1853" box="[93,159,508,529]" class="Aves" family="Aves (awaiting allocation)" genus="Crucirostra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aves (awaiting allocation)" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FFEE75E6FF69145C" box="[93,159,508,529]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">major</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, thereby designating it the 
<typeStatus id="7C5488149E48FF80FE4875E1FD91145C" box="[507,615,507,529]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">lectotype</typeStatus>
, and noted that it was tied together with its female. This female, 
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FEEA762CFDE71406" bold="true" box="[345,529,566,587]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">AMNH 456972</emphasis>
, would thereby become a 
<typeStatus id="7C5488149E48FF80FE9F7649FE3C1424" box="[300,458,595,617]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">paralectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FE5D764EFDCE1424" box="[494,568,596,617]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">
<taxonomicName id="64EF4D359E48FF80FE5D764EFDC21424" authorityName="C. L. Brehm" authorityYear="1853" box="[494,564,596,617]" class="Aves" family="Aves (awaiting allocation)" genus="Crucirostra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aves (awaiting allocation)" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">major</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
The other two specimens mentioned by Brehm are also 
<typeStatus id="7C5488149E48FF80FF217694FEC814E9" box="[146,318,654,676]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
: a second female collected on the 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FF0576B6FE60148C" box="[182,406,683,705]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1848-12-28">28 December 1848</date>
was cataloged as 
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FFEE76D3FEF91493" bold="true" box="[93,271,713,734]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">AMNH 456983</emphasis>
and was exchanged to ZFMK and the first-year male obtained on 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FDE376FCFEFF1554" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1848-02-12">12 February 1848</date>
is 
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FE997719FE291555" bold="true" box="[298,479,771,792]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">AMNH 456982</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A35036B69E48FF80FFC97738FDCA1237" blockId="76.[93,620,213,1147]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">
In the description, Brehm noted that the three specimens collected on the same day were collected on the 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FEEF7747FDCE153F" box="[348,568,861,883]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1847-12-28">28 December 1847</date>
, but the label on the two specimens still in AMNH, not in Brehm’s hand, is marked 
<date id="D75110769E48FF80FE617782FF621587" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" value="1847-12-27">27 December 1847</date>
and is labeled 
<taxonomicName id="64EF4D359E48FF80FEF777AFFF3D15A5" authority="Brm. The" authorityName="Brm. The" class="Aves" family="Aves (awaiting allocation)" genus="Crucirostra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aves (awaiting allocation)" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pityopsittacus">
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FEF777AFFD9D1587" box="[324,619,949,970]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">Crucirostra pityopsittacus</emphasis>
Brm. The
</taxonomicName>
28 December is perhaps the date on which he received it. 
<bibRefCitation id="C77E4B479E48FF80FE3277EAFD9D124B" author="Hartert, E." box="[385,619,1008,1030]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" pagination="4 - 63" refId="ref118974" refString="Hartert, E. 1918. Types of birds in the Tring Museum. A. Types in the Brehm Collection. Novitates Zoologicae 25: 4 - 63." type="journal article" year="1918">Hartert (1918: 11)</bibRefCitation>
thought the handwriting was perhaps that of Brehm’s son, Oskar; he also noted that Brehm’s name, 
<taxonomicName id="64EF4D359E48FF80FEA97052FEAA1210" authorityName="C. L. Brehm" authorityYear="1853" box="[282,348,1096,1117]" class="Aves" family="Aves (awaiting allocation)" genus="Crucirostra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aves (awaiting allocation)" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FEA97052FEAA1210" box="[282,348,1096,1117]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">major</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, is a junior secondary homonym of 
<taxonomicName id="64EF4D359E48FF80FF4F707CFDC11237" authority="Billberg, 1828" authorityName="Billberg" authorityYear="1828" box="[252,567,1125,1147]" class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Loxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="76" pageNumber="76" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">
<emphasis id="919BEAA49E48FF80FF4F707CFE7C1236" box="[252,394,1126,1147]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">Loxia major</emphasis>
Billberg, 1828
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
